OL,3,CCottage hospital ward to re-open after
OL,4,Csix month closure
OL,6,FA cottage hospital ward in Kent ,
OL,7,Fwhich closed in July because of unsafe
OL,8,Fstaffing levels, is due to re-open
OL,9,Fnext month.
OL,11,FThe 16 bed facility in Faversham
OL,12,Fprovides rehabilitation for patients
OL,13,Fto get regain their independence after
OL,14,Fan acute hospital stay.
OL,16,FHigh levels of nursing vacancies and
OL,17,Fstaff sickness were blamed for the
OL,18,Fclosure.
