OL,4,Csix month closure
OL,6,FKent Community Health Trust says after
OL,7,Fa successful recruitment campaign, it
OL,8,Fcan safely reopen to admissions on the
OL,9,F2nd December.
OL,11,FThe trust's chief executive, Mairead
OL,12,FMcCormick, said: "Our hospital
OL,13,Frecruitment campaign has been
OL,14,Fsuccessful and, with significant
OL,15,Fefforts made to onboard and induct our
OL,16,Fnew recruits for Faversham, we are
OL,17,Fconfident we will be able to safely
OL,18,Fstaff the ward.
